      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那人哇哇大叫，只骂：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖抬头见那人身披道袍，长须飘飘，正是长春子丘处机，心中大喜，叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
